metadata.name: Zen Interstellar #1
metadata.description: Zen Interstellar is a visionary art collection that melds the futuristic aesthetics of Astropunk with the timeless elegance of Japanese artistry. Embarking on an odyssey through the cosmic realm, this collection explores the delicate balance between technology and tradition, while uncovering the profound interconnectedness of the universe. Each piece serves as a gateway to introspection, invoking the ancient wisdom of the East and the boundless possibilities of the cosmos. Experience the transcendent fusion of ancient and avant-garde as you immerse yourself in Celestial Zenith, a journey that redefines the essence of beauty, unity, and the human spirit.
